        <num>27-2703</num>
        <heading>Store operator responsibilities</heading>
        <content>
          <p>* ยง 27-2703. Store operator responsibilities.\n  1. The operator of a store shall establish an at-store recycling\nprogram pursuant to the provisions of this title that provides an\nopportunity for a customer of the store to return to the store clean\nplastic carryout bags and film plastic.\n  2. A retail establishment that does not meet the definition of a store\nand that provides plastic carryout bags to customers at the point of\nsale may also adopt an at-store recycling program.\n  * NB There are 2 ยง 27-2703's\n</p>
